# Zoning Map Designer - Harita Hive Urban Planning Tool
# MIT License
#
# Create zoning plans with overlays (commercial, green, residential)
# Interactive design with regulatory compliance checking
#
# Features:
# - Interactive zoning map creation
# - Pre-built zoning templates
# - Regulatory compliance checking
# - Multi-layer overlay support
# - Automatic area calculations
# - Public comment integration
#
# Zoning Types:
# - Residential (R1, R2, R3, R4)
# - Commercial (C1, C2, C3)
# - Industrial (I1, I2, I3)
# - Mixed-use developments
# - Green spaces and parks
# - Special overlay districts
#
# Compliance Features:
# - Setback requirement validation
# - Height restriction checking
# - Density limit enforcement
# - Environmental constraint overlay
# - Historic district protection
#
# Export Formats:
# - PDF maps for public review
# - Shapefile for GIS systems
# - Web maps for online viewing
# - Legal descriptions for ordinances
#
# Usage:
# zoning-designer --create-project "Downtown Revitalization"
# zoning-designer --import-basemap parcels.shp --validate-compliance